== Public Baths (Sento) == * {{ill|Tsuruno-yu (Yamagata)|en|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuruno-yu (Yamagata)|qq=}} – A former sento (public bath) in Tsuruoka City, Yamagata Prefecture.
